    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">Publications</div>
  </div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Less is more: refinement proofs for probabilistic proofs"
    desc="Kunming Jiang, Devora Chait-Roth, Zachary DeStefano, Michael Walfish, Thomas Wies. IEEE S&P 2023."
